body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        An initiative describes the product roadmap at the highest level and is a collection of epics
        It usually takes a year to implement. Initiatives are not only related to software and defined by the management.
  - type: textarea
    id: outcome
    attributes:
      label: Initiative
      description: What is the strategic effort that will help us to achieve our goals? 
      placeholder: What is your initiative?
      value: "Revolutionize neurovascular procedures"
    validations:
      required: true
  - type: textarea
    id: epics
    attributes:
      label: Epic Breakdown
      description: Necessary epics to implement the initiative once they're created
      value: |
        Epic Link 1
        Epic Link 2
      placeholder: Link epic issues!
    validations:
      required: false
